  "title": "Audit Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Training and development opportunities</li>\n  <li>Performance-based bonus</li>\n  <li>Open door policy and positive work culture</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support the audit team to perform on-site fieldwork</li>\n  <li>Document and test clients’ internal control system</li>\n  <li>Internal audit, special projects, transaction services and due diligence work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma holder in Accountancy or equivalent professional qualification</li>\n  <li>ACCA Affiliate and ISCA Associate are greatly encouraged to apply.</li>\n  <li>Desire to make the profession a long-term career</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Special Skills:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidates should possess good command of English with excellent written and verbal communication skills, as well as interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Candidates must also be prepared to work in a multi-cultural environment and travel, particularly to Asian countries.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in an additional Asian Language is highly desired (to liaise with an additional Asian Language speaking associates)</li>\n  <li>Strong working knowledge of Microsoft Word and Excel is required.</li>\n</ul>",
